comment: Dragic (MIA) and Wade (MIA) maintain legal guarding position and make incidental contact with Carter-Williams (MIL) that does not affect his RSBQ. Any contact on the play is initiated by Carter-Williams.
Parker (MIL) and Winslow (MIA) make incidental contact with one another during rebounding.
Dragic (MIA) does not establish a legal guarding position outside of the restricted area prior to the start of Carter-Williams's (MIL) upward shooting motion.
Middleton (MIL) and Bosh (MIA) briefly engage and separate while attempting to establish position in the post.
Middleton (MIL) maintains his pivot foot until he releases his dribble.
Wade (MIA) maintains legal guarding position as he defends Middleton's (MIL) drive. Middleton slips as attempts to make his move and falls to the floor.
Wade (MIA) makes incidental contact with Middleton (MIL) as he attempts to go for the ball. Milwaukee is awarded a timeout prior to the simultaneous possession between Wade and Middleton.
Bosh (MIA) legally contests Antetokounmpo's (MIL) driving dunk attempt.
Winslow (MIA) sets the screen on Middleton (MIL) and gives him room to avoid the contact. The two players briefly engage and separate following the screen.
LHH shows that Wade (MIA) makes contact with Antetokounmpo's (MIL) arm that causes him to lose control of the ball.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) commits a take foul on Wade (MIA).
Wade (MIA) maintains legal guarding position and legally contests Middleton's (MIL) jump shot attempt.
Carter-Williams (MIL) commits a take foul on Wade (MIA).
Wade (MIA) and Middleton (MIL) briefly engage and separate away from the ball.
Middleton (MIL) commits a take foul on Wade (MIA).
